Detailed Description template<typename Key, typename Mapped, typename Tag, typename Node_Update, typename Policy_Tl, typename _Alloc>class __gnu_pbds::basic_branch< Key, Mapped, Tag, Node_Update, Policy_Tl, _Alloc >
A branched, tree-like (tree, trie) container abstraction.
Template Parameters
Key
Key type.
Mapped
Map type.
Tag
Instantiating data structure type, see container_tag.
Node_Update
Updates nodes, restores invariants.
Policy_TL
Policy typelist.
_Alloc
Allocator type.
Base is dispatched at compile time via Tag, from the following choices: tree_tag, trie_tag, and their descendants.
Base choices are: detail::ov_tree_map, detail::rb_tree_map, detail::splay_tree_map, and detail::pat_trie_map.
